props.disabled: Prevents the item from becoming active when using the “next” and “prev” buttons or the `toggle` method.
props.eager: Will force the components content to render on mounted.
props.transition: The [custom transition classes](https://v3.vuejs.org/guide/transitions-enterleave.html#custom-transition-classes) used when the component progressing through items.
props.value: The value used when the component is selected in a group. If not provided, the index will be used.
